Package net.akami.mask.alteration

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CalculationAlteration<T>
    Definer of the behavior of an expression modifier, in the context of mathematical calculations.
    CalculationCanceller<T>
    One of the two core objects of the alteration system, provided by the library.
    IOCalculationModifier<T>
    One of the two core objects of the alteration system, provided by the API.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CalculationCache
    A CalculationCanceller added by default in the library that avoids calculation repetitions.
    DegreeUnit
    Specifies that angles are given in degrees.
    GradientUnit
    Specifies that angles are given in gradients.
    PowExpansionLimit
    Decides what the maximal numeric exponent is before canceling the power calculation.
